properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Mexico Beach out 20 NM; Coastal Waters from Mexico Beach to Apalachicola out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 11 at 5:28AM EST until February 11 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one to two miles.

* WHERE...Nearshore Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County
line to Apalachicola out 20 nautical miles.

* WHEN...Until 3 PM CST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 PM CST THIS AFTERNOON
